Skincare Actives 101! 

Here are some of my favourite skin care actives and this is everything you need to know 💖✨

1. HYALURONIC ACID :
TonyMoly’s Vital Vita 12 Ampoule 
- Attracts and binds with water to retain moisture in skin
- Replenishes moisture and suppleness in skin
- Boosts skin’s regenerative and rejuvenating effects that smoothens skin
2. GLYCOLIC ACID : Pixi Glow Tonic 
- Exfoliates dead skin cells from the skin’s surface
- Brightens and smoothens complexion
- Fades hyperpigmentation
3. RETINOL : Murad Youth Renewal Serum 
- Improves cell turnover and prevents fine lines and wrinkles
- Keeps pores unclogged and reduces acne breakouts
- Brightens dull and tired skin
4. AHA - I.E, Alpha Hydroxy Acid :
Mario Badescu’s AHA Botanical Body Soap 
- Exfoliates and brightens skin
- Brightens and smoothens complexion
- Fades hyperpigmentation
